snippet.title: My Rusty Submarine - Global Game Jam 2020 Submission
snippet.description:
Gameplay of  a two player couch co-op game I made for the global game jam 2020 with the theme "repair".

Game and source code can be downloaded here:
https://soerbgames.itch.io/my-rusty-submarine
